        },
        {
            "id": 7,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   This Feline woman is not some no-name.",
                "name": "Hellagur"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 8,
            "prop": "Decision",
            "attributes": {
                "options": "But she still was no match for you.;General, are you hurt?",
                "values": "1;2"
            },
            "targetLine": {
                "option1": "line9",
                "option2": "line9"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 9,
            "prop": "Predicate",
            "attributes": {
                "references": "1;2"
            },
            "endOfOpt": false
        },
        {
            "id": 10,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   Don't worry. Her henchmen were mediocre at best. After ensuring your safety, it was a fairly simple matter for me to retreat.",
                "name": "Hellagur"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 11,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   However, I might know a thing or two about the identity of that bodyguard.",
                "name": "Hellagur"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 12,
            "prop": "Decision",
            "attributes": {
                "options": "Her identity?;Do you mean...",
                "values": "1;2"
            },
            "targetLine": {
                "option1": "line13",
                "option2": "line13"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 13,
            "prop": "Predicate",
            "attributes": {
                "references": "1;2"
            },
            "endOfOpt": false
        },
        {
            "id": 14,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   Columbian, Feline, female, silver hair, amber eyes, and a black crossbow. She's both a mercenary and an assassin.",
                "name": "Hellagur"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 15,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   For a hitman, being famous is nothing to be proud of, but the truth is that her feats were simply too astonishing.",
                "name": "Hellagur"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 16,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   For example, she once wiped out an entire clan in Columbia. It was a powerful clan as well. Gradually, over a few years, its important figures met violent ends one after another until the entire clan crumbled into nothingness.",
                "name": "Hellagur"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 17,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   Another example - she once hunted down an entire patrol group. This patrol was notorious for killing people at Columbia's border. Calling themselves 'Conquerors of the Barbarians,' their violence towards other races brought about many tragedies.",
                "name": "Hellagur"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 18,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   After a single month, they fled into the mountains but were slain left and right until only one member, disabled and incoherent, managed to make it back to the city.",
                "name": "Hellagur"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 19,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   The last example is the man who told me these stories.",
                "name": "Hellagur"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 20,
            "prop": "Decision",
            "attributes": {
                "options": "What happened to him?;Keep going. I'm not intimidated.",
                "values": "1;2"
            },
            "targetLine": {
                "option1": "line21",
                "option2": "line21"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 21,
            "prop": "Predicate",
            "attributes": {
                "references": "1;2"
            },
            "endOfOpt": false
        },
        {
            "id": 22,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   I'll get to the point. He has a scar going from his left shoulder to his right heel.",
                "name": "Hellagur"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 23,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   Cold-blooded killers are abound here, and I'm one of them.",
                "name": "Hellagur"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 24,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   Of course, this particular woman has been missing for some time.",
                "name": "Hellagur"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 25,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   But if my hunch is correct, and they're the same person, then things are about to get real ugly.",
                "name": "Hellagur"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 26,
            "prop": "Decision",
            "attributes": {
                "options": "The waters here are a lot murkier than I expected.;Is Ceylon being tricked?",
                "values": "1;2"
            },
            "targetLine": {
                "option1": "line27",
                "option2": "line27"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 27,
            "prop": "Predicate",
            "attributes": {
                "references": "1;2"
            },
            "endOfOpt": false
        },
        {
            "id": 28,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   The mayor might not be blind to all of this.",
                "name": "Hellagur"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 29,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   As a matter of fact, I wouldn't even be surprised if the mayor was the one who hired her.",
                "name": "Hellagur"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 30,
            "prop": "Character",
            "attributes": {}
        },
        {
