        },
        {
            "id": 33,
            "prop": "Decision",
            "attributes": {
                "options": "Ceylon?!;How long have you been here...",
                "values": "1;2"
            },
            "targetLine": {
                "option1": "line34",
                "option2": "line34"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 34,
            "prop": "Predicate",
            "attributes": {
                "references": "1;2"
            },
            "endOfOpt": false
        },
        {
            "id": 35,
            "prop": "Character",
            "attributes": {
                "name": "char_188_helage_1"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 36,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   Miss Ceylon, you don't have to eavesdrop.",
                "name": "Hellagur"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 37,
            "prop": "Character",
            "attributes": {
                "name": "char_188_helage_1",
                "name2": "char_348_ceylon_4#8",
                "focus": 2.0
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 38,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   I... I just wanted to get some water for you...",
                "name": "Ceylon"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 39,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   Mister Hellagur, when did that mercenary begin her career, and when did she go missing?",
                "name": "Ceylon"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 40,
            "prop": "Character",
            "attributes": {
                "name": "char_188_helage_1",
                "name2": "char_348_ceylon_4#8",
                "focus": 1.0
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 41,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   She had made a name for herself even before I was discharged.",
                "name": "Hellagur"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 42,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   As for when she disappeared, I'd say about a year ago, after that clan was annihilated.",
                "name": "Hellagur"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 43,
            "prop": "Character",
            "attributes": {
                "name": "char_188_helage_1",
                "name2": "char_348_ceylon_4#8",
                "focus": 2.0
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 44,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   ...Schwarz had been taking care of me, up until six years ago.",
                "name": "Ceylon"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 45,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   But one day, she suddenly told me my father needed her for something, and just left. After that, I only saw her when she'd pick me up over Christmas.",
                "name": "Ceylon"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 46,
            "prop": "Character",
            "attributes": {
                "name": "char_188_helage_1",
                "name2": "char_348_ceylon_4#3",
                "focus": 2.0
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 47,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   B-but, I'm sure she was just in a bad mood, plus she was just following orders. There's no way she's a cold-blooded killer!",
                "name": "Ceylon"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 48,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   Furthermore, are you implying that my father is somehow behind Cronin's actions?!",
                "name": "Ceylon"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 49,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   I don't believe it!",
                "name": "Ceylon"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 50,
            "prop": "Character",
            "attributes": {
                "name": "char_188_helage_1",
                "name2": "char_348_ceylon_4#3",
                "focus": 1.0
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 51,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   I won't jump to conclusions. However, I must remind you that even the people you trust most cannot solely look out for your interests.",
                "name": "Hellagur"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 52,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   Whether she trusts you or not is none of my concern. All I know is, I would never mistake those scars inflicted by Ursusian weapons. The squad that did that to her are now buried deep underneath the snow.",
                "name": "Hellagur"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 53,
            "prop": "Character",
            "attributes": {
                "name": "char_188_helage_1"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 54,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   The situation should be clear to you, Doctor.",
                "name": "Hellagur"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 55,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   If the City Council also has a hand in circulating false information about the volcano, then we should stay out of this.",
                "name": "Hellagur"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 56,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   Miss Ceylon, you should also try to see the truth.",
                "name": "Hellagur"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 57,
            "prop": "Character",
            "attributes": {
                "name": "char_348_ceylon_4#9"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 58,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   I... I need to calm down.",
                "name": "Ceylon"
            }
        },
